{"tid":592677,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"長洲覆核王指民建聯=民主建國聯盟","createTime":"2018-03-14T11:34:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-14T12:17:02.000Z","uid":5843,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2f92118f5909ff07887afa07d2b85de61380fdc9","tid":592677,"uid":5843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T11:34:25.000Z","msg":"有「長洲覆核王」之稱的郭卓堅今早到高院申請司法覆核，要求法庭撤銷在立法會九西補選中獲勝的民建聯鄭泳舜。郭指其所屬政黨主張<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"> 「民主建國</span></span>」，即等同推行港獨、分裂國家，違反《基本法》第104條宣誓及聲明條例。郭透露今晨凌晨4時許收到匿名電話留言，對方指「殯儀館留晒位畀你，好快啲入去。」<br />\n<br />\n郭指民建聯全名為「民主建港協進聯盟」，打着愛國口號卻暗中推動港獨，表明若港府以香港眾志主張「民主自決」而撤銷周庭參選資格，則應一視同仁地以民建聯主張「民主建國」、「民主建港」為由撤銷鄭的議員資格，否則難以服眾。郭批評港島區選舉主任鄧如欣撤銷周庭參選資格的決定越權，指鄧無權對參選人作政治審查<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hk.nextmedia/posts/10156557909797448\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhk.nextmedia%2Fposts%2F10156557909797448&d=5EFcCi6GraevK3nzQ%2F85icP%2FddU7lKBqZb2OVh9Tir8%3D&h=57d5b894\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hk.nextmedia/posts/10156557909797448</a><br />\n<br />\n啫係話港獨派畀人DQ都抵撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1063c07887d9708132134b8b3411a63a589b0943","tid":592677,"uid":5843,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T11:42:59.000Z","msg":"民主黨2014年已經咁勇武<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/14/194234_38413b9c23b3939db474b39940cc7283.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F14%2F194234_38413b9c23b3939db474b39940cc7283.png&h=ca590dfd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4f9be14d3814457803fb66bbc71fdb255a3445fb","tid":592677,"uid":34103,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T11:49:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"235238e673726e17d2f8392bb430c7